{"tid":398388,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"選舉日形同虛設！新加坡首位女總統哈莉瑪自動當選","createTime":"2017-09-13T07:11:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T17:07:23.000Z","uid":57786,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9941686eb253e61a73107c88e3ace5c520d2dd04","tid":398388,"uid":57786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T07:11:44.000Z","msg":"今年新加坡總統選舉第一次實行了保留馬來族群的新制度，結果卻形成了一個無人競爭、甚至無須選民投票，總統候選人就可以自動當選的奇怪現象，也就是說，本次參選的馬來裔候選人、前國會議長哈莉瑪(Halimah Yacob)將在沒有任何競爭的情況下，也不用透過選民投票的程序，只要如期交付表格就可以順利、自行宣布當選成為新加坡首位女總統，同時也是新加坡第8任總統。<br />\n<br />\n美國媒體CNN也關注了這個特別的新加坡選舉制度，報導指出下周末23日是新加坡總統選舉的日期，但是選民卻沒有選擇的機會，只能投給唯一一個符合馬來族群保留資格的候選人，就是前國會議長哈莉瑪。CNN認為新加坡總統選舉的確讓少數族群馬來裔候選人得到保留，確保少數族裔也能代表國家出任總統一職，但是不可諱言的，新制度同時說明了這是一場很有爭議的選舉。"},{"pid":"2e9e84006e6a6474a2302a5f44a9e061e305ab30","tid":398388,"uid":57786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T07:12:48.000Z","msg":"現年63歲的哈莉瑪曾在2013年擔任新加坡國會議長，成為新加坡史上第1位女性國會議長，今年8月初，她為了參選下屆總統，因此宣布辭去國會議長和議員的職務，全力投入競選活動。由於新加坡國會在2016年11月修憲，規定如果少數族裔連續5屆(共30年)沒擔任總統，之後一屆就會保留給該族裔，確保少數族裔也能代表國家形象，而過去5屆馬來裔候選人都未能在競選過程中脫穎而出，因此本屆總統選舉就啟用了新的制度，這也是新加坡修憲之後，首次實行新規定，將總統大位保留給馬來裔候選人。<br />\n<br />\n儘管本次新加坡總統選舉還有其他2名馬來裔候選人申請參加，但是經過新加坡選舉委員會鑑定結果，認為他們無法成為合格的參選者，公開宣布他們的身分、資格不符，最後只有發出1張合格證書給哈莉瑪，也就是說，哈莉瑪將在沒有其他候選人競爭的情況下，能夠順利交付登記參選表格，同時自行宣布當選下屆總統，即使有總統選舉日，選民依然無從選擇其他候選人。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡是一個多種族國家，居民以華人、馬來人和印度人為主。新加坡總統為虛位元首，不需要擔負政治責任，也無須行使行政權。新加坡總理職務才是政治要職，有實際的參政權。<br />\n<br />\n(中時電子報)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20170913002594-260408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20170913002594-260408&d=Fiapx9xV0uLnJffjTeDtImMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=e38fbb5e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20170913002594-260408</a>"},{"pid":"8f3eae3e76037c311442710c89efb4788e199d22","tid":398388,"uid":93784,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T07:17:19.000Z","msg":"新加坡總統為虛位元首，不需要擔負政治責任，也無須行使行政權。新加坡總理職務才是政治要職，有實際的參政權。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dca5c6873e2c5be6448060541849af9cb1410a7","tid":398388,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T07:19:02.000Z","msg":"嚇死"},{"pid":"5ac8a47259fdcde3c564f10fb22b09afacc601f4","tid":398388,"uid":57705,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T07:25:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"632565ddf0cbe7e0becddb8e9bfc8718391818ac","tid":398388,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T07:27:35.000Z","msg":"民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b1943a37196d5bd25d869a8e965aea965b6ed37","tid":398388,"uid":143241,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T07:30:09.000Z","msg":"咪又係人民行動黨玩鳩曬"},{"pid":"1af97dda5f631208334c9ad4b9423ec4747363e3","tid":398388,"uid":16970,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T07:30:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔止選舉虛設<br />\n總統個位本身都如同虛設</blockquote><br />\n新加坡總統係有一定憲制權力嘅, 之不過大部分時間都唔會用, 同英女皇一樣."},{"pid":"9bbaadbd95bfba95cfefa854b4a6b267157b44da","tid":398388,"uid":26752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T07:32:24.000Z","msg":"@真文學院毒男 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc6f81f4004da67387149111ad9c880d22eb0ae3","tid":398388,"uid":30085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T07:32:59.000Z","msg":"回西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41b1aa93ebf953bd966207378f944355e492a1af","tid":398388,"uid":60545,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T08:35:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新加坡一向冇，而新加坡人亦都認為民主冇乜必要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a5dd318da745249ed30a1f4ac3a3b37a5872122","tid":398388,"uid":143241,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T08:39:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新加坡一向冇，而新加坡人亦都認為民主冇乜必要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你畀著香港人人都住千幾二千呎嘅屋,生活基本需要政府都照顧,一定冇人出嚟屌政府"},{"pid":"37357a568c07673c82a4c1a5fd50616fcc64279c","tid":398388,"uid":57786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T09:19:59.000Z","msg":"Called Mdm Halimah Yacob to congratulate her on becoming Singapore&rsquo;s 8th President. Mdm Halimah has been a unionist, community leader, MP, Minister of State, and Speaker. She will bring to the Presidency her long experience working with Singaporeans from all walks of life, and championing workers and disadvantaged groups. <br />\n<br />\nThe President is the apex of our political system and the symbol of our multi-racial, multi-religious nation. I am confident that Mdm Halimah will fulfil her role with distinction.<br />\n<br />\nI also thank Mr Salleh Marican and Mr Farid Khan for offering themselves as candidates. It can&rsquo;t have been an easy decision for them and their families, knowing the media attention and public scrutiny this would attract. They respected the Constitution and conducted themselves with propriety and decorum. They did not confuse people with wild promises that exceeded the remit of the President, which had happened before. I thank them also for accepting the Presidential Elections Committee&rsquo;s decisions. This is the way to make our democratic processes work properly and in the interest of Singaporeans.<br />\n<br />\nMdm Halimah will be sworn in tomorrow. I hope all of us will support her as our next President. I look forward to working with her to serve Singaporeans and the nation. &ndash; LHL"},{"pid":"4614f68b2e480603c1e5713e6f576787b421ca14","tid":398388,"uid":57786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl